{
  "texts": [
    "RQ2: Stimuli.",
    "Regarding the stimuli used to arouse recall, video recordings of the learning process have gained tremendous popularity.",
    "While some changes have occurred during the evolution of SR methods, such as the improvement of video stimuli and the integration of physiological feedback data.",
    "Optimizing video stimuli.",
    "Video recordings are a widely popular type of stimuli in educational SR research, as evidenced by nearly 70% of the reviewed studies (173 articles) that utilized them."
  ]
}